metadata.name: AL & SPICA_The Fallen
metadata.description:
First 1/1 NFT of Glitch Manga series which you can find PFP collection in The_Punix Opensea either.

Foundation would be the platform to mint super premium NFT from the collection. 
----------------------------------------------
AL [The professor] and SPICA [The idol]
Main characters in the series.

All characters were all dead. They stuck in a dark world afterlife, began to fall into despair with glitch fx. Lost all memories. Ready to born a new life
However, they did not want to.
